        "number": 8,
        "text": "How great Thou art"
      }
    ]
  },
  "stanzas": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "O Lord my God"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "When I in awesome wonder"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "Consider all the worlds Thy Hands have made"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "I see the stars"
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "I hear the rolling thunder"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "Thy power throughout the universe displayed"
        }
      ],
      "number": 1
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "When through the woods"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "And forest glades I wander"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "And hear the birds sing sweetly in the trees"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "When I look down"
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "From lofty mountain grandeur"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "And see the brook and feel the gentle breeze"
        }
      ],
      "number": 2
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "And when I think"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "That God His Son not sparing"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "Sent Him to die I scarce can take it in"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "That on the Cross"
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "My burden gladly bearing"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "He bled and died to take away my sin."
        }
      ],
      "number": 3
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "When Christ shall come"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "With shouts of acclamation"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "And take me home"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "What joy shall fill my heart"
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "Then I shall bow"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "In humble adoration"
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "text": "And there proclaim"
        },
        {
          "number": 8,
          "text": "“My God, how great Thou art!”"
        }
      ],
      "number": 4
    }
  ],
  "title": "How Great Thou Art"
}
